description:
VPN client-side toolset.

Open-source opinionated VPN client implementing major VPN protocols.

Supported protocols:

  • Shadowsocks (Outline)
  • Shadowsocks over WebSocket
  • Shadowsocks over Cloak

Config format

Dobby consumes “subscription” / “dynamic keys” as YAML over HTTPS. The full up-to-date format (with examples) is documented in the project README:

https://github.com/DobbyVPN/DobbyVPN/blob/main/README.md
